question_text: I understand this tool is not a diagnosis and a clinician will review.

Describe what’s wrong in this area.
Has it been improving, worsening, or unchanged?
How severe is it right now? (0–10)
Is it improving, worsening, or unchanged?

Select any medical conditions you have (or 'none').
Have you had any surgeries or hospitalizations?
